      "description": "## The Button Atom\n\nLet's look at a real atom - the Button!\n\n### What can you customize?\n- **Size**: Extra small, small, medium, large, extra large\n- **Color**: Primary (red), secondary (gold), green, blue, etc.\n- **Style**: Solid, outline, ghost (transparent)\n- **Loading**: Show a spinner while something is happening\n\n### Using the Button:\n```tsx\n<Button size=\"md\" variant=\"primary\">\n  Book Now\n</Button>\n\n<Button size=\"sm\" variant=\"secondary\" buttonStyle=\"outline\">\n  Learn More\n</Button>\n\n<Button loading={true}>\n  Please wait...\n</Button>\n```\n\n### One component, many uses!\nThe same Button code is used for \"Login\", \"Book Now\", \"Add to Cart\", and every other button in the app."
