      "description": "## The Rating Atom\n\nShows star ratings like: ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÜ (4 out of 5)\n\n### Two modes:\n\n**Read-only mode** (for display):\n```tsx\n<Rating value={4.5} readOnly />\n// Shows: ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ‚òÖ¬Ω\n```\n\n**Interactive mode** (user can click):\n```tsx\n<Rating \n  value={rating} \n  onChange={(newValue) => setRating(newValue)} \n/>\n// User can click to set rating\n```\n\n### Why a dedicated Rating component?\n- **Consistency** - All ratings look the same\n- **Accessibility** - Works with keyboard\n- **Reusable** - Used for homestays, guides, products"
