      "description": "## The Price Atom\n\nDisplays money amounts in Indian Rupees (‚Çπ).\n\n### Features:\n\n**Basic price:**\n```tsx\n<Price amount={2500} />\n// Shows: ‚Çπ2,500\n```\n\n**With time period:**\n```tsx\n<Price amount={2500} period=\"per night\" />\n// Shows: ‚Çπ2,500 per night\n```\n\n**With discount (original price crossed out):**\n```tsx\n<Price amount={1800} originalAmount={2200} />\n// Shows: ‚Çπ1,800 ‚Çπ2,200 (2,200 is crossed out)\n```\n\n### Why a dedicated Price component?\n- **Formatting** - Handles commas (2,500 not 2500)\n- **Currency** - Always shows ‚Çπ symbol\n- **Consistency** - All prices look the same across the app"
