      "description": "## What are Organisms?\n\nOrganisms are **large sections** of a page. They're made of molecules and atoms.\n\n### The Navbar Organism\n\nThe navigation bar at the top of every page contains:\n- Logo (clickable, goes to home)\n- Navigation links (Homestays, Guides, etc.)\n- **SearchBar** molecule\n- Cart icon with item count\n- User menu (login/profile)\n\n### Key difference from molecules:\n- Molecules are **small and flexible** (use anywhere)\n- Organisms are **specific page sections** (navbar, footer)\n\n### Organisms in our app:\n\n| Organism | What it is |\n|----------|------------|\n| **Navbar** | Top navigation |\n| **Footer** | Bottom links |\n| **Hero** | Landing page banner |\n| **ListingGrid** | Grid of cards |\n| **BookingWidget** | Booking sidebar |"
