      "description": "## üìã To Do: Build a Molecule from Atoms\n\nLet's practice atomic design by creating a `TestimonialCard` molecule.\n\n---\n\n### Step 1: Plan What Atoms You'll Use\nThis molecule will combine:\n- **Avatar** atom (user photo)\n- **Rating** atom (star rating)\n- **Icon** atom (quote icon)\n\n### Step 2: Create the Props File\nCreate `src/components/molecules/TestimonialCard/TestimonialCardProps.ts`:\n```typescript\nexport interface TestimonialCardProps {\n  name: string;\n  avatar?: string;\n  rating: number;\n  quote: string;\n  location?: string;\n}\n```\n\n### Step 3: Create the Component\nCreate `src/components/molecules/TestimonialCard/TestimonialCard.tsx`:\n```typescript\nimport { Avatar, Rating, Icon } from '../../atoms';\nimport { TestimonialCardProps } from './TestimonialCardProps';\n\nexport function TestimonialCard({\n  name,\n  avatar,\n  rating,\n  quote,\n  location\n}: TestimonialCardProps) {\n  return (\n    <div className=\"card bg-base-100 shadow-md\">\n      <div className=\"card-body\">\n        <Icon name=\"format_quote\" className=\"text-primary text-3xl\" />\n        <p className=\"text-base-content/80 italic\">\"{quote}\"</p>\n        <div className=\"flex items-center gap-3 mt-4\">\n          <Avatar src={avatar} alt={name} size=\"sm\" />\n          <div>\n            <p className=\"font-semibold\">{name}</p>\n            {location && (\n              <p className=\"text-sm text-base-content/60\">{location}</p>\n            )}\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <Rating value={rating} readOnly size=\"sm\" />\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n```\n\n### Step 4: Create Index and Export\n```typescript\n// index.ts\nexport { TestimonialCard } from './TestimonialCard';\nexport type { TestimonialCardProps } from './TestimonialCardProps';\n\n// Add to molecules/index.ts\nexport * from './TestimonialCard';\n```\n\n---\n\n## ‚ö†Ô∏è Watch Out For\n\n| Issue | Cause | Solution |\n|-------|-------|----------|\n| Atoms not found | Wrong import path | Use relative path: `../../atoms` |\n| Layout broken | Missing flexbox classes | Add `flex`, `gap-*` utilities |\n| Card too wide | No max-width | Add `max-w-sm` or container |\n| Avatar not showing | Invalid image URL | Add fallback/placeholder |\n\n---\n\n## ‚ùå Common Errors\n\n| Error Message | What It Means | How to Fix |\n|---------------|---------------|------------|\n| `Avatar is not exported` | Atom not exported | Check atoms/index.ts |\n| `Cannot find module '../../atoms'` | Wrong path | Verify folder structure |\n| `rating.toFixed is not a function` | Rating is string not number | Ensure rating prop is number |\n| Component renders nothing | Missing return statement | Check JSX is returned |\n\n---\n\n### ‚úÖ Checklist\n- [ ] Identified atoms to use (Avatar, Rating, Icon)\n- [ ] Created props interface with correct types\n- [ ] Imported atoms correctly\n- [ ] Composed atoms with proper layout\n- [ ] Added responsive styling\n- [ ] Exported from molecules index\n- [ ] Tested with sample data"
